# INSTALLATION MANUAL - SpotiPOD v0.0.3

SpotiPOD – Record your Spotify playlists easily! �

Want to save your favorite Spotify songs without any hassle? SpotiMy lets you automatically record your playlists in high quality and organize them on your device.

✅ Record entire playlists with Cover in minutes.
✅ Save files in popular MP3 format.
✅ Organize your music with names and metadata.
✅ Easy to use, no complex settings.
✅ Backup forever you playlist if you dont have internet access.

Download now and keep your favorite music forever!

# Why Spoti My...

The idea starts because I currently listen to all my music in playlists directly from spotify. But the problem arises because spotify arbitrarily deletes the songs and this affects especially when I want to listen to a song that I really liked and it is no longer in my playlist :( . That is why I wrote spoti my to make a backup in my local of all my music on spotify and to be able to identify and download the ones that are not there from other sources. And if one day I get fed up with Spotify, I'll have all my music to take with me anywhere.

